articles.title: Steve Harley, Cockney Rebel and ‘Make Me Smile’ Singer, Dead at 73 - Rolling Stone
articles.description: Steve Harley, singer for the British glam rock act Cockney Rebel and their 1975 hit "Make Me Smile (Come Up and See Me)," has died at the age of 73.
articles.content:
